  "synopsis": {
    "native": "Nina et Madeleine, deux retrait\u00e9es, sont profond\u00e9ment amoureuses l\u2019une de l\u2019autre. Aux yeux de tous, elles ne sont que de simples voisines vivant au dernier \u00e9tage de leur immeuble. Au quotidien, elles vont et viennent entre leurs deux appartements et partagent leurs vies. Personne ne les conna\u00eet vraiment, pas m\u00eame Anne, la fille attentionn\u00e9e de Madeleine. Jusqu\u2019au jour o\u00f9 un \u00e9v\u00e9nement cruel fait tout basculer.",
    "english": "Nina and Madeleine, two retired women, have been secretly deeply in love for decades. From everybody\u2019s point of view, including Madeleine\u2019s family, they are simply neighbors living on the top floor of their building. They come and go between their two apartments, sharing the tender delights of everyday life together. Until the day their relationship is turned upside down by an unexpected event leading Madeleine\u2019s daughter to slowly unveil the truth about them."
